                                2002 - index
       National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration Current Events

   OSEI snow cover products (SNW) include multichannel color composite
   imagery showing snow cover, usually after a significant storm system
   has passed or when snow cover amounts change rapidly because of
   unseasonably warm weather.

       The following image files have recently been added to the Snow
                                 archive...

